headline: Fair Isaac Corporation Announces Date for Reporting of First Quarter Fiscal 2026 Financial Results
summary: BOZEMAN, Mont., January 14, 2026--Global analytics software leader FICO (NYSE: FICO), will announce its first quarter fiscal 2026 results on January 28, 2026, after the market closes and will host a conference call on January 28th at 5:00 p.m. Eastern time (4:00 p.m. Central/ 2:00 p.m. Pacific).
